                    <span>On target and once again the living proof that it is not necessary to have the perfect product, rather the perfect sales pitch, to be successful in selling. No matter if we are talking about the 1880s or the twenty-first century, if you can create the right interest, right sales tactics and create the demand, you will be successful. When you finish this book, you will come to realize that the only person holding you back is none other than yourself. Gitomer serves up a winner that stands heads and shoulders above the other "How to sale your product" books. Buy it, read it, and make your mark.</span>
                  
