                    <span>This book gives the reader the opportunity to learn selling at the feet of John Patterson, the original master salesman of America. Gitomer does a great job bringing Patterson's principles into this era. I recommend this book to every sales associate out there!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Not enough meat</div>
